c" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/reading@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/reading@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/reading@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/reading@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/reading@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/reading@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2025">Reading＆Leeds</a>宣布了第二波艺术家将在2025年版中演出，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/limp-bizkit">Limp Bizkit</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/d-block-europe">D-Block Europe</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heartworms">Heartworms</a> 。在下面查看更新的账单。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/reading-leeds-festival-2024-review-best-bits-liam-gallagher-lana-del-rey-fontaines-dc-3787423">2024年阅读节：夏天最后一次大井口的最神奇的时刻</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的双节日版将在8月21日至24日之间举行。回到12月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2025-line-up-announced-headliners-tickets-3819354">确认了加入该阵容的第一波艺术家</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">Chappell Roan</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/TRAVIS-SCOTT">Travis Scott，Travis Scott</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">将我带给我地平线</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/HOZIER">Hozier</a>都被确认为头条新闻。</p><p>现在，组织者已经确认了更多的名字加入了该法案，包括Nu-Metal Pioneers Limp Bizkit，他们将登上主要阶段，以执行诸如“ Break Stuff”，“ Nookie”，“ My Way”等经典阶段。他们的场景将导致谢菲尔德金属巨头的标题插槽带给我地平线。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGlXhEaItGL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 