需的东西。”</p><p>他继续说：“对我来说，这只是乐队不可思议的声明，只是想取悦他们的歌迷。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/bring-me-the-horizon-reading-festival-2022-review-setlist-photos-3299213">他们上次在2022年打球</a>绝对是非凡的。他们肯定会登上它。”</p><p> 2024年巨大的分期付款<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/blink-182-reading-2024-review-photo-setlist-3786510">，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-oasis-reunion-noel-3787153">Liam Gallagher</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-3787168">，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lana-del-rey-reading-2024-live-review-setlist-photos-3786852">Lana del Rey</a> ，Fred <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/gerry-cinnamon-live-at-reading-2024-review-photos-setlist-3786511">再次</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/fred-again-reading-festival-2024-review-photos-setlist-3786905">。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。</a>您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/reading-leeds-festival-2024-review-best-bits-liam-gallagher-lana-del-rey-fontaines-dc-3787423">在此处找到该版本的NME最佳时刻</a>列表。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2025-limp-bizkit-d-block-europe-heartworms-and-nell-mescal-lead-huge-line-up-additions-3842012">Reading＆Leeds 2025年：Limp Bizkit，D-Block Europe，Heartworms和Nell Mescal Lead Lead巨大的阵容增加</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
