4.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP-main@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>吉布森（Gibson）与英国服装品牌MERC联手创建了限量版的Mod-Indreps商品运行。查看下面的集合。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-kapichi-and-madness-suggs-talk-new-single-zombie-nation-and-the-impact-of-the-specials-terry-hall-3593758">Kid Kapichi和Madness“ Suggs谈论新单曲“僵尸民族”和特惠的Terry Hall的影响</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这家标志性的吉他品牌已与该公司加入了新的Merc X Gibson Capsule Collection，该系列专门在伦敦的Gibson车库有限的时期可用。</p><p>该系列设计的目的是强调音乐与时尚之间的牢固联系，包括五个。这些是“传奇人物哈灵顿夹克”，“ Luthier Polo衫”，“桥梁连帽运动衫”，“即兴T恤”和“ Tone” T恤。</p><p> “ MERC很高兴与Gibson合作，我们很荣幸能展示一个胶囊系列，以体现本质并庆祝这两个品牌的丰富遗产，” MERC董事总经理Sas Alavi在一份新声明中说。 “该系列经过精心设计，可以无缝地融合Merc和Gibson的美学，同时吸引现代敏感性，从而创造出与时尚爱好者和吉他爱好者都产生共鸣的作品。” </p><figure id="attachment_3841991" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Gibson X Merc与Kid Kapichi合作" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-KP@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841991" class="wp-caption-text"> Gibson X Merc与Kid Kapichi合作。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>该系列还借助上升的朋克摇滚乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-kapichi">Kid Kapichi</a>宣布，他们被选为“当选择一位在2025年体现朋克摇滚生活方式并展示胶囊系列的艺术家时，他们是自然而然的选择”。</p><p> Kid Kapichi和Blue Stragglers一起参加了本周早些时候在Eastcastle Street的Gibson车库，以推出新范围，并在商店提供了各种表演。</p><p> “很高兴与两个标志性品牌紧密合作。随着时间的流逝，我们自然而然地陷入了吉布森吉他的圈速，因为我认为他们的声音是我们创造的音乐无与伦比的，” Kid Kapichi说。 “因此，与他们合作多个项目是一种荣幸。</p><p> “当我们被要求与新合作合作时，说&#39;是&#39;是一个简单的决定。 Merc总是为60年代的美好重现美丽的物品。与音乐和乐队密切相关的一种，我们一生都热爱我们的一生。我们受到了这些乐队的影响，衣服也与之齐头并进。”</p><p>查看下面范围的更多图像，并在<a href="https://www.gibson.com/en-GB/garage-london?srsltid=AfmBOop5H3oH5xcxYRFN-zNmoCaabwyElWkGm3qjRlJTAIzvRfVvfoN_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">伦敦的吉布森车库</a>中独家找到完整的收藏。 </p><figure id="attachment_3841992" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841992" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841992" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-jacket@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841992" class="wp-caption-text"> Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3841994" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841994" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841994" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-tee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841994" class="wp-caption-text"> Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3841995" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841995" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841995" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Gibson-Merc-hoodie@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841995" class="wp-caption-text"> Gibson X Merc合作。学分：吉布森</figcaption></figure><p>伦敦的吉布森车库于去年2月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-page">吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">布莱恩·梅（Brian May）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tony-iommi">托尼·艾莫米（Tony Iommi）</a>的帮助下首次开业。</p><p>它的灵感来自纳什维尔旗舰分公司（Nashville Flagship Branch），并有300多个吉他，以及楼下的现场音乐空间和订购定制吉他的量身定制柜台。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brian-may-tony-iommi-and-james-bay-join-jimmy-page-to-launch-gibson-garage-london-3592070"><em>NME</em>参加了该商店的首次预览，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">LED Zeppelin</a> Icon Jimmy Page参加了会议，并与该品牌分享了新的合作 - 推出了他标志性的1971 Doubeneck的复制品。</p><p>最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Queen">皇后</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-brian-may-launches-new-12-string-acoustic-guitar-with-gibson-i-wish-my-dad-was-here-to-see-this-3839464">布莱恩·梅（Brian May）本月与制造商合作推出了全新的限量版12弦原声吉他，回到了场地。</a></p><p>他解释说：“这把吉他的想法是当我需要12弦的巡回演出时，而我习惯的那个吉他的想法并没有在舞台上表演。” “如果您看一下这把吉他，它的美丽以及声音的美丽，并看一下吉他中的科学，看看这把吉他的技术和工艺已经有多少。吉布森（Gibson）能够以象征意义的方式将宇宙放在上面，而《星球》（Planet Mercury）就在这里，这对我的一个总是与我同在的朋友有点点头。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gibson-teams-up-with-merc-to-launch-limited-edition-mod-inspired-merch-collection-3841990">Gibson Post与MERC合作，推出了限量版Mod Indrepired Merch Collection，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
伟哥男孩分享古怪的新单曲“ Uno II” https://www.nme.com/news/music/viagra-boys-shaviagra-boys-share-eccentric-new-new-new-single-uno-ii-ii-listen-herere-new-herere-new-single-uno-uno-iuno-ii-3841951?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = viagra-boys-shaviagra-boys-boys-share-centric-new-new-single-uno-iuno-io-ii-listen-listen-listen-herere-nerere-new-single-single-uno-iiTom Skinner Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:22:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsPost-PunkPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3841951 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伟哥男孩按照图片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>它的灵感来自塞巴斯蒂安·墨菲（Sebastian Murphy）和他的狗一起去兽医的旅行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/viagra-boys-shaviagra-boys-share-eccentric-new-single-uno-ii-listen-herere-new-single-uno-ii-3841951">伟哥后的邮报分享偏心的新单曲“ Uno II”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伟哥男孩按照图片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ViagraBoysnewsingle-Uno-II-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/viagra-boys">伟哥男孩</a>分享了一张名为“ Uno II”的全新单曲 - 您可以在下面听它。</p><p>这首歌将出现在斯德哥尔摩后朋克乐队的第四张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/viagra-boys-announce-new-self-titled-album-with-chaotic-single-man-made-of-meat-3831371">“ Viagr Aboys”</a>上，该专辑将于4月25日通过自己的唱片公司Shrimptech Enterprises发行。<a href="https://viagr-aboys.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处预订/预先保存</a>。</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-festival-2024-viagra-boys-on-new-music-influencing-kings-of-leon-and-beef-with-the-hives-3787032">Viagra Boys on new music, influencing Kings of Leon and beef with The Hives</a></strong></li></ul><p> “&#39;Uno II&#39; redirects vocalist Sebastian Murphy&#39;s take on conspiratorial anxiety – shifting from human meat bags to finding it embodied in his beloved dog,” a description reads.</p><p> The singer&#39;s pet, an Italian greyhound, had frequently visited the vets over the course of a year due to dental problems. This led Murphy to wonder what his dog could be thinking – and he put pen to paper.</p><p> Murphy explained: “He goes to this place, then wakes up in some weird room, and he&#39;s missing his teeth.”</p><p> “ <em>I seem like such a bitch/ When I talk about Swedish politics</em> ,” the frotman sings atop a shuffling drum beat. The tune also boasts whispers of flute and a sweeping electric guitar part. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="伟哥男孩-UNO II（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9kWgvEKIo4c?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> shrimptech sent our star reporter to a dog show in czechia, but the croatian veterinarian bogdan might have other plans for us</p><p> uno ii, the second single from viagr aboys, out now: <a href="https://t.co/FMaQNZXJNL">https://t.co/FMaQNZXJNL</a> <a href="https://t.co/6xakOWgFJi">pic.twitter.com/6xakOWgFJi</a></p><p> — viagr aboys (@ViagraBoys) <a href="https://twitter.com/ViagraBoys/status/1895036150667989029?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 27, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p></p><p> Embodying his pooch, Murphy states in the first verse: “ <em>&#39;I found a crouton underneath a futon&#39;/ Mamma said, I couldn&#39;t eat it &#39;cause all my teeth are gone/ My personality is based on food now/ Take it from Bogdan, he&#39;s my veterinarian/ His folks are from Croatia/ They&#39;ve been through some shit, man</em> .”</p><p> The single is accompanied by an official music video in which Murphy – portraying a “star reporter” – is sent on assignment to cover a seemingly innocent dog show in Eastern Europe. However, he soon discovers that he is under constant surveillance and being shadowed by some mystery forces. Watch it all unfold above.</p><p> &#39;Uno II&#39; follows on from Viagra Boys&#39; recent track <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/viagra-boys-announce-new-self-titled-album-with-chaotic-single-man-made-of-meat-3831371">&#39;Man Made Of Meat&#39;</a> – which was partly inspired by the band&#39;s experience on the road with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a> . They&#39;ll <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-of-the-stone-age-announce-full-line-up-and-second-date-for-sheffields-rock-n-roll-circus-buy-tickets-3840169">support Josh Homme and co. again this summer at Rock N Roll Circus in Sheffield</a> .</p><h3> <strong>The full tracklist for Viagra Boys&#39; &#39;Viagr Aboys&#39; is:</strong></h3><p> <strong>&#39;Man Made of Meat&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;The Bog Body&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Uno II&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Pyramid of Health&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Dirty Boyz&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Medicine for Horses&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Waterboy&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Store Policy&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;You N33d Me&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;Best in Show Pt. iv&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;River King&#39;</strong> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Viagra Boys at Reading Festival 2024 on new music, inspiring Kings of Leon and beef with The Hives" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cEgiewYtkcE?start=108&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/viagra-boys-cave-world-review-3265079"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-festival-2024-viagra-boys-on-new-music-influencing-kings-of-leon-and-beef-with-the-hives-3787032">During an interview with <em>NME</em> at last year&#39;s Reading Festival</a> , Viagra Boys explained that their new music would incorporate “a little bit of everything, hopefully”.</p><p> “We&#39;re gonna see where it ends up,” Murphy said. “I think there&#39;s a little bit of all sorts of genres in there, hopefully – excluding maybe R&amp;B and stuff 