cribing him as “The Greatest” and Francis Ford Coppola called him “inspiring and magnificent in his work and complexity”.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gene-hackman-fans-are-sharing-his-emotional-1972-oscars-speech-in-memory-of-the-late-actor-3841959">Gene Hackman fans are sharing his emotional 1972 Oscars speech in memory of the late actor</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
